Class BasicStats

java.lang.Object
BasicStats
public class BasicStats extends Object
Creates a simple GUI that includes: - a text field and a button that allows the user to enter numbers. - a button that allows the user to clear all entered numbers. - a panel with labels and text fields for count, median, mean, and max. - a text area that shows all numbers. - a button that allows you to undo the last number added.
